    "This can help to reduce fraud, increase transparency, and improve trust between supply chain partners.",
    "Additionally, blockchain technology can be used to create a more efficient supply chain by automating certain processes.",
    "For example, smart contracts can be used to automatically trigger transactions or payments when certain conditions are met.",
